  "title": "Principal/ Senior Clinical Pharmacist #HZO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: Up to $9K</p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead development and implementation of new clinical pharmacy services</li><li>Provide advanced clinical pharmacy care in a state-of-the-art facility</li><li>Design and execute training programs for emerging pharmacists</li><li>Mentor and nurture the next generation of pharmacy professionals</li><li>Collaborate with multidisciplinary teams to create innovative healthcare solutions.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min. <strong>PharmD </strong>or any relevant field</li><li>Min. 3-4 years relevant clinical experience</li><li>Proven track records in developing new clinical skills or training program</li><li>Preferably experience with PHI </li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: <a href=\"mailto:melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><br />All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence<br />Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)<br />R2197564<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />99C4599</p>",
